high_descs: Turn around and walk until you are in the middle of the white counter and then turn right to face the wall and counter.
Pick up the fork on the counter that's holding the knife upright.
Turn right and walk to the fridge so you are facing it.
Open the fridge and put the fork in the glass that's behind the tomato.
Pick up the glass with the fork in it and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk a few steps and turn right and face the counter so you are in front of the loaf of bread.
Put the cup with the fork in it on the counter near the edge directly in line with the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around to face the opposite wall and walk forward, then turn to face the counter on your right.
Pick up the fork next to the photograph.
Turn to your right and walk forward, then turn to face the black refrigerator on your left.
Open the refrigerator and place the fork in the black cup behind the tomato.
Take the cup with the fork in it out of the refrigerator and shut the door.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the counter with the photographs and bread on it.
Place the cup and fork on the edge of the counter in front of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it on the counter in front of the bread.

high_descs: Turn around, walk passed the fridge, and then turn right to find the fork on the counter.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Turn right and turn into the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge and place it in the cup behind the tomato.
Take the cup out of the fridge and close it.
Turn left, walk passed the fridge, and turn right to find the bread on the counter.
Place the cup in front of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place the fork in a cup from the fridge.
